{% block guidance_3 %}

    <ul>
<li>不要来学校。</li>
<li>如果您已经和公共卫生人员（例如接触者追踪调查员/<em>contact tracers</em>）有过交流，请遵循他们的指导意见。</li>
<li>如果您还没有收到公共卫生指导意见，请在返回校园之前联系<a href="https://www.publichealthmdc.com">麦迪逊与戴恩郡公共卫生部（<em>Public Health Madison &amp; Dane County</em></a>）。</li>
</ul>
  
{% endblock %}


{% block guidance_4 %}

    <ul>
<li>不要来学校。</li>
<li><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/if-you-are-sick/quarantine-isolation.html">开始14天的自我隔离。</a></li>
<li>如果出现<a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/symptoms-testing/symptoms.html"><em>COVID-19</em>症状</a>，联系您的医护人员进行评估或是进行<em>COVID-19</em> 检测。</li>
<li>在结束14天的自我隔离并确认没有<em>COVID-19</em>症状后才可以返回校园。</li>
</ul>
<p>参考由疾病控制中心（<em>Centers for Disease Control</em>）发布的<a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/if-you-are-sick/index.html?CDC_AA_refVal=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fcoronavirus%2F2019-ncov%2Fhcp%2Fguidance-prevent-spread.html">额外指导意见</a>。</p>
  
